mal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係邊度訂?</blockquote><br />\nGoogle store<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前一路冇貨訂唔倒，有日女朋友翻翻下工見倒有即訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話要幾多日先運到黎?<br />\n同埋香港係應該買美版定英版個NETWORK先冇事?"},{"pid":"801432fb4ada1e203aa8933e7bf5c9345638efe1","tid":461370,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>訂左xl，生日果日到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係邊度訂?</blockquote><br />\nGoogle store<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前一路冇貨訂唔倒，有日女朋友翻翻下工見倒有即訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話要幾多日先運到黎?<br />\n同埋香港係應該買美版定英版個NETWORK先冇事?</blockquote><br />\n你爬下文先啦, 我根本搵唔到兩個版本有乜分別, 今次英版美版既Model Number 係完全一樣, 加上官網show出黎既頻譜顯示, 英美版係無分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4563a6262151a2954c24f2ff02ecee30b4a5e887","tid":461370,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n冇美國地址 美國信用卡 點換？</blockquote><br />\n我同Google個邊溝通個陣係有問可唔可以香港寄<br />\n佢需要美國地址同電話先換到<br />\n我有個美國朋友所以借咗佢地址電話用<br />\n但係其實後來上網check兩樣都可以租到來用再揀個方式寄去Google同埋運過來香港<br />\n<br />\n我都比較好彩<br />\n寄返去美國個陣冇比人扣起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我諗其實如果你factory reset部機又冇乜可疑就會過<br />\n最後佢就換咗比我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但係個美國朋友寄來到依家都未收到勁不安<br />\n希望冇尾香</span>"},{"pid":"3d81bf1c0b32eba9